SAVE_TYPE - at.peirleitner.core.util.database.TableType
Table name for SaveType
SaveType - Class in at.peirleitner.core.util.database
A SaveType is used to separate data inside the database to avoid overrides.
Example: The User may have A$ on SaveType 1, as well as B$ on SaveType 2 - On both SaveTypes the same Database/Table is used.
